{"thag2.26:0.1":"Theragatha 2.26 ","thag2.26:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.26:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.26:0.4":"Punnamasattheragatha ","thag2.26:1.1":"“Panca nivarane hitva, ","thag2.26:1.2":"yogakkhemassa pattiya; ","thag2.26:1.3":"Dhammadasam gahetvana, ","thag2.26:1.4":"nanadassanamattano. ","thag2.26:2.1":"Paccavekkhim imam kayam, ","thag2.26:2.2":"sabbam santarabahiram; ","thag2.26:2.3":"Ajjhattanca bahiddha ca, ","thag2.26:2.4":"tuccho kayo adissatha”ti. ","thag2.26:2.5":"… Punnamaso thero …. "}